info: 0 INT 4 PBU 24/54 416 yards 77.2 TACK 71.2 COV. 6’2 212 with 32 ¼ arms.
pros: Great size at 6’2 and over 200. Great in press, can squeeze receivers out of routes. Solid ability to sink his hips and stop. Great tackler, good size and physicality.
cons: Not the best athlete, a little slow out of breaks. Not agile, a shifty WR could separate easily. No INT in the last 2 years.
