CB Terrell Smith Minnesota 74
info: 2 INT 4 PBU 31/53 341 yards 70.1 TACK 78.7 COV. 6’1 204 with 32 7/8 arms.
pros: Has the ideal size speed combo, good length and good testing numbers. Good physicality, good at getting hands on and tough to get away from. Solid tackler, strong aggressive corner.
cons: Was not very good for 4 years before a 5th year breakout. Not very smooth in and out of breaks, would like to see it more fluid. Not a sticky corner, WR can eaily fool him and get off him.
