CB Riley Moss Iowa 73
info: 8 INT 1 PBY 45 tackles 74.4 TACK 81 COV. 6’0 192 with 30 3/8 arms.
pros: White CB, you never see that. Good eyes in zone, see’s the field and play develop well. Solid ball skills, goes and attacks the ball.
cons: Not a big or long corner. Not the best athlete, wont jump off the screen. Long speed is missing, gets stacked easily.
take: Moss should be a team that’s primarily zone coverage, he’s not the best athlete.
